title: Rust Nightly, Issue with Diesel 1.3.3 (Won't Compile)
body:
When trying to build Diesel 1.3.3 using rustc 1.30.0-nightly (4141a4079 2018-09-25), I get the following error:

```
Compiling diesel v1.3.3
     Running `rustc --crate-name diesel /home/vagrant/.cargo/registry/src/github.com-1ecc6299db9ec823/diesel-1.3.3/src/lib.rs --color always --crate-type lib --emit=dep-info,link -C debuginfo=2 --cfg 'feature="32-column-tables"' --cfg 'feature="bitflags"' --cfg 'feature="default"' --cfg 'feature="diesel_derives"' --cfg 'feature="postgres"' --cfg 'feature="pq-sys"' --cfg 'feature="with-deprecated"' -C metadata=c2d89ec2449070fc -C extra-filename=-c2d89ec2449070fc --out-dir /vagrant/target/debug/deps -L dependency=/vagrant/target/debug/deps --extern bitflags=/vagrant/target/debug/deps/libbitflags-90a38bd8f3b92b88.rlib --extern byteorder=/vagrant/target/debug/deps/libbyteorder-481c2a066ed0920b.rlib --extern diesel_derives=/vagrant/target/debug/deps/libdiesel_derives-0bd0e577a6f349d9.so --extern pq_sys=/vagrant/target/debug/deps/libpq_sys-543d0e07817bf8dc.rlib --cap-lints allow -L native=/usr/lib`
error: Could not compile `diesel`.

Caused by:
  process didn't exit successfully: `rustc --crate-name diesel /home/vagrant/.cargo/registry/src/github.com-1ecc6299db9ec823/diesel-1.3.3/src/lib.rs --color always --crate-type lib --emit=dep-info,link -C debuginfo=2 --cfg 'feature="32-column-tables"' --cfg 'feature="bitflags"' --cfg 'feature="default"' --cfg 'feature="diesel_derives"' --cfg 'feature="postgres"' --cfg 'feature="pq-sys"' --cfg 'feature="with-deprecated"'-C metadata=c2d89ec2449070fc -C extra-filename=-c2d89ec2449070fc --out-dir /vagrant/target/debug/deps -L dependency=/vagrant/target/debug/deps --extern bitflags=/vagrant/target/debug/deps/libbitflags-90a38bd8f3b92b88.rlib --extern byteorder=/vagrant/target/debug/deps/libbyteorder-481c2a066ed0920b.rlib --extern diesel_derives=/vagrant/target/debug/deps/libdiesel_derives-0bd0e577a6f349d9.so --extern pq_sys=/vagrant/target/debug/deps/libpq_sys-543d0e07817bf8dc.rlib --cap-lints allow -L native=/usr/lib` (signal: 9, SIGKILL: kill)
```
